{"id":232896093,"title":"20200115，予妳","content":"讓夢見妳成為習慣  不去掙扎打散\n讓想妳成為習慣  不去侵擾逃避\n儘管現在不在身旁了  \n\n綿綿細雨纏在身旁\n揮不開的矇矓  是想念\n\n冷冷的風刮過\n刺骨的痛  是存在\n\n左手邊的空位留給了妳\n等待時間催化\n等待時間允許\n等待那該完成的事\n\n妄想吧！\n放任吧！\n繼續期盼吧！\n\n那才有繼續走下去的動力\n儘管現在不在身旁了","excerpt":"讓夢見妳成為習慣  不去掙扎打散，讓想妳成為習慣  不去侵擾逃避，儘管現在不在身旁了，綿綿細雨纏在身旁，揮不開的矇矓  是想念，冷冷的風刮過，刺骨的痛  是存在，左手邊的空位留給了妳，等待時間催化，等","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-15T12:37:06.126Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T12:37:06.126Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["心情","創作","隨筆"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"思爾天想","department":"m.e3952","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}